    MapLoader
    Loads levels from a *.skb file and provides them to the SokochanEngine Created by Vittorio on 25-Oct-16.
    SokochanEngine
    This class organises all the other core classes of the Sokoban engine.
    SokochanGrid
    This class wraps a two dimensional array of Tiles (that will be implemented as an array of arrays in Java, because of the lack of thereof) and provides a series of methods to retrieve GridObjects and Tiles placed in a position.
